author: The Critical Drinker
description: In some of the least shocking news this year, The Last Jedi director Rian Johnson confirms what everyone else has known for years - that his fabled Star Wars trilogy will no longer be happening. Join me as I look back on his... erm, interesting career with Star Wars.
title: Bye, Rian. No More Star Wars For You
